Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:10.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.12,0:00:20.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.61,0:00:39.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.88,0:00:46.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.09,0:00:54.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.47,0:00:59.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.84,0:01:07.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.31,0:01:14.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:21.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:28.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:31.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,As planned...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:34.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,...with communication cables\Nintact, Chor Tempest...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:36.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,...will descend as low as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:40.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and protect the Ruins from attack\Nby the Shoukoku-highland forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:49.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,The enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.59,0:01:55.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Funeral
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.17,0:02:05.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,This sibylla's spirit is\Nbound by chains of sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:10.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, both the merciful\NTempus Spatium, as well as Kyuukoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:13.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,...are prepared to\Nforgive and accept her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:37.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,But why the heck was Anglas lying\Ndead inside an ancient Simoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:39.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,That day, there's no\Nquestion that she...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:45.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:55.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,They never found so much as\Na bone fragment in the debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:08.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,This sibylla has just received\Nthe divine grace of Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:11.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now that she is about to set off\Non a new journey, let us pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:40.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,She was a highland priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.13,0:03:43.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not only that, but a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:45.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,How can we hold a funeral\Nfor her on the Arcus Prima?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:47.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,The high priestess felt it\Nwas the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:49.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,And how did the\Nmilitary council feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.47,0:03:52.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,That since the Highlands and\NShoukoku are now allies...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.68,0:03:55.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it wouldn't do to send\Neven the remains back to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:57.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,And yet they're so full\Nof mutual animosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:04:01.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, it seems they do agree\Non the most unlikely thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:04.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that's what\Ncauses trouble for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:19.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,You won't get a\Nbreeze sitting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:23.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:27.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,To think that you'd start a\Nconversation with me... Who knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:34.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,What happened at the Ruins...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:37.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:44.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:49.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:56.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,We found the Spring\Ninside the Ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:58.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,And Onasia was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:01.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:04.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the Spring itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:06.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just like Grandpa said!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:16.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,And then we found Anglas, who\Nsurely perished in that explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:17.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,...inside an ancient Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:21.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking that Anglas\Nwent there herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.77,0:05:22.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.77,0:05:23.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,In that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:25.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the moment the Simoun exploded...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:29.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,...she went to a different world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:30.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,A different...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:31.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,...world?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:37.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just when we thought we were\Nback home on the Arcus Prima...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:39.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,...all these weird\Nthings started happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:41.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,At least give us a\Nlittle downtime, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:45.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no time to get comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:48.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're to go to the maju\Npool right after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:50.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,I do like majus...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:52.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but not if we're\Nbeing ordered to do them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:55.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, isn't that Neviril\Nand Aer over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:01.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, so they managed to make up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:03.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, make up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:05.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril was just having\Na hissy fit on her own!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:22.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Aer. What do you mean by...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:26.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's something Grandpa told me once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:34.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, hurry up! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:37.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Grandpa, come on! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:38.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:41.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is as far as I can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:42.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:44.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,You go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.22,0:06:49.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Getting old means making\Nmore and more choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:52.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,And with every choice you make...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:55.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,...you erase all\Nother possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:06:57.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:01.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simoun will show\Nyou where you're headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:04.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where I'm headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:09.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,To a different world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:15.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,What my grandpa meant by\Nthat, I still don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.38,0:07:18.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,But Grandpa was\Nalways yearning for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:22.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer, is that why you never\Nwanted to choose your gender?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,The helical motors...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:31.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Said to manipulate\Nboth time and space...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:34.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought it was\Nno more than a story...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:37.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to strengthen the\Nmystery of the Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:39.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:41.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and yet nowhere."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:45.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,If that's true of Onasia...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:47.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and true of Anglas...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:49.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and true of the Simouns...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:52.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:54.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it's true of Rimone\Nand Dominüra as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:02.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,What we just talked about...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:04.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's keep it between ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:05.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,So we're going to share a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:08.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just the two of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:11.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:18.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you attend\NAnglas's funeral?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:19.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those are the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:21.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,A priestess from a\Nlowly family like mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:24.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,...has no right to\Nattend a holy ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:26.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,B-But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:27.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,You joined us the other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:28.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,You joined us the other time.\NThings are different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:30.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our leaders are in turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:34.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,But they allowed an enemy\Npriestess's funeral to be held here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:36.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don't sound\Nlike yourself at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:38.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought you\Nliked that Anglas girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:41.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:42.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:47.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,I knew I'd have to face at least\Nthis level of discrimination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:48.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:51.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,The only reason I got to the rank\Nof Simoun sibylla was because...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:54.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I had the backing\Nof the vice chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:56.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:59.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,But the vice chancellor has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:01.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:04.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,He's nothing but a\Nsenile old geezer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:06.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute, Mamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:10.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,I enjoyed our time on the Messis,\Nespecially that mouse stew I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:10.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:13.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Watching all you oh-so-noble\Npriestesses taste that stew...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:16.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I thought, "Hey, they're\Njust the same as me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:17.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right. We're the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:21.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:22.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're not the same after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:30.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.42,0:09:37.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:40.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,The maju pool is under the\Njurisdiction of the chancellors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:43.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Should you set foot in this area...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:43.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the high priestess will...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:44.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the high priestess will...\NIt doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:00.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Military Councilor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,You must forgive us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:05.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but we can't have\Nso many observers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:07.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,It will disturb our prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:09.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,A maju is not a prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:10.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:13.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is battle practice,\NSibylla Aurea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:16.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:20.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,What Chor Tempest is\Ncurrently capable of...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:23.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ri Majon with the\Nmost destructive power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:42.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,What a lovely wake\Nthey're creating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:48.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Dandelion Ri Majon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:50.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,The one that harms no one...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that leads no one astray...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:54.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the one for ceremonies...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:55.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the one for ceremonies...\NHmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:11.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's better this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:14.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I didn't make the\Nwrong choice after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:18.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Entrusting Aer to\Nbecome Neviril's pair...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:22.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's all good\Nbecause of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:25.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,You have no clue whatsoever!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:29.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Could the judgment of\Nsomeone who's been asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:32.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,...be less questionable\Nthan your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:35.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thinking someone\Nlike you can protect her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:37.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is gross arrogance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:40.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:41.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,...let Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:46.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.82,0:11:48.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I might have made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:53.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,With you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:55.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:00.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:03.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I might have made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.57,0:12:10.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to pair up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.61,0:12:12.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.88,0:12:15.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,After all, I'm the one who\Nshould be protecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:51.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dismantle a Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:57.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd hear those\Nwords from anyone else but you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:12:58.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Sibylla Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:03.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Forget about that day, Waporif.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:08.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's the last warning\NI'll be giving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:12.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,But how could I ever forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:14.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Without something to believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:17.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,...none of us can even\Nplant our feet on the earth."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's what you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:21.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have you found\Nsomething to believe in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:35.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,What should I believe in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:51.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have ordered\Nthe maintenance crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to dismantle the ancient\NSimoun as you instructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:57.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dismantling a divine vessel.\NHow sacrilegious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:00.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which is more sacrilegious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:03.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Allowing our holy Tempus Spatium\Nto be tainted by outsiders?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:07.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,The topic for discussion today...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.56,0:14:10.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is what to do about\Nthat enemy air base.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:14.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,As most of the ancient Simouns\Nare now in the enemy's hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:17.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I believe it would be\Ndangerous to send Chor Tempest...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:18.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,...out on a reconnaissance mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:18.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,...out on a reconnaissance mission...\NThen when would you deem it safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:20.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then when would you deem it safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:24.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,I understand your concern for\Nyour daughter's well-being.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:27.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,However, should another\Nincident occur...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:31.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,...next time for sure, you won't have\Na leg to stand on, Vice Chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.38,0:14:35.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who is paired up with Sibylla Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,That would be Sibylla Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:40.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Out of all the members\Nof Chor Tempest...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:42.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,...she has no parallel\Nas an auriga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:44.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I recall, her grandfather was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:50.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even so, she herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:52.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:54.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:03.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where are you taking her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:05.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:07.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anglas's funeral is long over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:10.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't she have been committed\Nto the earth as soon as possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:12.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is an order from\Nthe military councilor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:14.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,The military councilor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.13,0:15:18.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,How dare you debase a departed\Nspirit. I won't allow this to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:33.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Once you've left the cockpit of a\NSimoun, a woman is utterly powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,It would be too\Ndangerous to sit back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:49.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and do nothing about\Nthat mobile air base.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:54.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are hereby sending Chor Tempest\Non a reconnaissance mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:56.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Messis shall serve\Nas the relay point...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:16:00.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? Just when we finally got away\Nfrom that musty, old rust bucket!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:03.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am happy to welcome\Nyou all back, Sibyllae!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:05.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:07.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,And if we discover the base?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:10.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,That will be left to\Nyour discretion, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:11.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,As for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:15.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I do believe you have the\Ncapacity to blow it up at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:20.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,As both Sibylla Dominüra and Sibylla\NRimone are missing in action...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:23.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we will have to\Nreadjust your pairings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:27.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Paraietta and Sibylla Kaim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:32.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Alty and Sibylla Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:35.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Roatreamon and Sibylla Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:37.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:39.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and Sibylla Mamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:43.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Yun and Sibylla Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:47.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's been decided that you two will\Nsit out this particular mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:52.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NWhy am I being left behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:56.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer is my pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:16:58.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,You'll have to convince me as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:03.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:07.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, don't cause\Nany more trouble for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:26.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NYou can't sleep, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:28.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:31.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your maju this afternoon.\NIt was magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:33.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:40.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,How about... a dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:43.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm not in the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:49.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:08.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd\Nstand up for Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:11.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not that I've opened\Nup to her completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.47,0:18:15.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,But by coming face\Nto face with Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:16.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I'm also coming face\Nto face with Amuria...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:19.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,...meaning I'm facing\Nup to myself as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:26.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,That may have been my\Ngreatest fear all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:31.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I was just trying to avoid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.62,0:18:34.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've allowed you all to\Nhumor me far too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:37.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,So let me humor you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:40.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:44.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can go ahead\Nand lean on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:48.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,But at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:50.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I won't make it to a different world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:50.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I won't make it to a different world.\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:53.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nothing, never mind\Nwhat I just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:01.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,A different world, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:05.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,If it's a different\Nworld you long for...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:06.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,...then I'll show you one now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:08.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Parai...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:01.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:03.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:05.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun's fast asleep, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:09.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just thought you might\Nbe too nervous to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:12.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pairing up with Sibylla Aurea...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:17.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I always saw that as the\Nfastest way to achieve my goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:18.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:21.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I don't want you\Nto get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:21.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.30,0:20:25.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Deep down, I do want the rest\Nof you to see me as an equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:26.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:28.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,...not for the same\Nreasons as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:31.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:35.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I really want to be\Nfriends with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.45,0:20:40.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:43.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,So stop saying things like,\N"We're friends," will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:46.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just a matter of\Nhow you feel about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:48.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:53.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina, do you want me\Nto sing you a lullaby?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:56.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mean the one\Nyou sang for Rimone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:20:59.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!\NI'm not a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:05.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hear the echo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:06.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry, not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:07.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry, not listening.\N...of the swirling light...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:12.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,...of the swirling light...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.42,0:21:24.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,...bringing us tales of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:36.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Proof that an\Neternal world exists...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:43.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,...shall be revealed\Nby Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:46.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rocking gently until\Nwe awake tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:48.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why do you think they\Ntook you off the mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:50.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have a pretty good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:51.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,You do, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.09,0:21:52.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:54.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's something that bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.86,0:21:55.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.69,0:21:57.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:21:59.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,...because I promised not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.10,0:22:01.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.30,0:22:02.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's wise of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.53,0:22:07.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Promises are made\Nto be kept after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.05,0:22:22.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've got to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.69,0:22:23.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,As do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.40,0:22:48.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.15,0:22:52.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.38,0:22:59.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:07.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.84,0:23:19.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to get closer to you.\NI want to feel your pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.94,0:23:25.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.12,0:23:28.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:33.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.12,0:23:38.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:44.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the\Nsky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.53,0:23:47.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.97,0:23:53.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.64,0:23:59.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.29,0:24:06.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.72,0:24:06.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued\NNeviril's Simoun is shot down...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.96,0:24:08.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril's Simoun is shot down...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.03,0:24:13.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and forced to make an emergency\Nlanding on Shoukoku's aerial base.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.40,0:24:15.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.83,0:24:16.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.77,0:24:17.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla\NSibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.73,0:24:20.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla
